{
  "stem": "7094.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "But-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] it's there all the time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "I live with it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "And my main preoccupation originally was to put it behind.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "You know, my husband was also a survivor, but he escaped from Warsaw in 1939/40.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "He had a fantastic story of survival.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "And he could talk about it easier, because his was like adventure story.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "You know, he went through Russia, to Japan, to Canada.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "He came-- he was in the army.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "I could never talk about it so much.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "We decided-- because I would break down.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "And very often-- we decided, at that stage, that we will put this behind us, that we want-- the purpose of having a family was to rebuild the family.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "And the purpose of that was also that if we have a family, we give them an equal chance.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "We give them-- that we don't want to bring them up under the shadow of our experiences, because very often the second generation suffers very much.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "And if there is any achievement that I can comfort myself with my life, it is that I brought up two sons who were normal.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 82,
      "text": "I don't consider anything else-- that they were normal human beings.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 83,
      "text": "Because I've seen things which went very wrong, because automatically you are very possessive.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 84,
      "text": "You concentrate all your love on your-- every mother does, but this is exaggerating.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 85,
      "text": "You know, your insecurity, you hand over to the next generation.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 86,
      "text": "Your fears, your insecurity, the way you handle babies.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 87,
      "text": "Well, I've managed to do that reasonably well.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 88,
      "text": "So I feel that at least my children-- I've never talked to my children properly about my experiences.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 89,
      "text": "They were too young.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 90,
      "text": "My grandchildren-- I talk to them more than to my children.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
